A khajiit companion, archer but can use one handed weapons if nessecary.

descriptionHtml:
A khajiit companion, archer but can use one handed weapons if nessecary.
No quest for getting him, and he\'s fully voiced with skyrim default voices.
He\'s close to riverwood, further up the river on the opposite side where there is no road, he\'s got a tent and a wood chopping block there. He\'s a skilled with archery, sneak, and one handed.
author: falloutforlife
